    <values>
        <field>Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Event Monitoring is not capturing ReportExport or DashboardExport event types. Bulk data extractions via Reports and Dashboards are not being logged.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Impact__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Bulk data exports via Reports and Dashboards are a primary insider threat exfiltration vector. Without export event logging, an insider can export the entire customer database with no audit trail.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Enable Report Export and Dashboard Export event types in Setup &gt; Event Manager. Create a Transaction Security policy to alert on exports exceeding a configurable row count threshold.</value>
